Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.86,0:00:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你就这么喜欢丝袜吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.04,0:00:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,居然凑得这么近在看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.59,0:00:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,来，好好看清楚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.86,0:00:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,鸡巴是不是在撸动啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.83,0:00:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,想看堇的丝袜吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.40,0:00:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你到底有多变态啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.82,0:00:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,那，你看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.78,0:00:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,给你看这个，你就乖乖撸你的肉棒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.50,0:00:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你的鸡巴变成什么样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.90,0:01:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你就那么喜欢你那鸡巴吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.66,0:01:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,让我摸摸看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.78,0:01:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,变得这么硬了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.12,0:01:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,想让我怎么玩弄这根肉棒呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.36,0:01:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不老实回答的话，我可不陪这根肉棒玩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.92,0:01:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,真是敏感的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.30,0:01:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,光是看到丝袜就兴奋成这样了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.80,0:01:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,那要是直接摸这根鸡巴，会变成什么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.30,0:01:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,想被怎么对待？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.96,0:01:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,想让我舔吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.06,0:02:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,快说“请帮我舔”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.14,0:02:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不求我的话可不行，真是无可救药的肉棒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.92,0:02:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.24,0:02:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,好好地撸起来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.76,0:02:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你很喜欢吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.90,0:02:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.06,0:02:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,有好好握着吗？你的肉棒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.12,0:02:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,撸起来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.96,0:02:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢的对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.80,0:02:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,想狠狠地摩擦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.99,0:02:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,蹭在这丝袜上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.19,0:02:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.42,0:02:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,鸡巴蹭在这里好像很舒服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.22,0:02:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,想尽情地蹭吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.04,0:02:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,肉棒涨得硬邦邦的真可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.29,0:02:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,想要得停不下来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.12,0:03:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里玩弄的话，会有多舒服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.48,0:03:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,好想要肉棒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.02,0:03:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,真想要肉棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.60,0:03:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,把肉棒给我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.14,0:03:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,想把它狠狠地蹭在丝袜上对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.32,0:03:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,想怎么样？想被舔得湿哒哒的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.60,0:03:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你在想象吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.34,0:03:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,鸡巴已经涨得这么硬了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.42,0:03:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你在想象什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.36,0:03:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,是被吸吮着，还是被丝袜套弄着？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.38,0:04:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,是哪一种？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.68,0:04:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,好想要肉棒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.80,0:04:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,要我玩弄你那根硬邦邦的肉棒吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.12,0:04:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,是被吸得啧啧作响吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.28,0:04:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,要不要一边舔一边撸呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.34,0:04:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样？正被怎么对待呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.98,0:04:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.36,0:04:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,很美味吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.58,0:04:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,看，嘴巴小穴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.26,0:04:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,很美味吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.82,0:04:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,自己在撸动呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.50,0:05:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,看，这是堇的真空丝袜哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.25,0:05:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,让肉棒勃起得更厉害一点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.99,0:05:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,看，你喜欢这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.48,0:05:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.06,0:05:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,想在这里蹭来蹭去吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.53,0:05:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,很想要吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.60,0:05:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,想被夹在这里吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.20,0:05:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,想被夹在这里对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.06,0:05:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,变热了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.06,0:06:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,想要吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.22,0:06:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,想被这大腿夹住对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.72,0:06:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,想让肉棒被这样狠狠地套弄对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.95,0:06:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,已经相当湿了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.72,0:06:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,想舔舔我的阴蒂吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.16,0:06:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,想撸管吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.97,0:07:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,想舔吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.82,0:07:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.38,0:07:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,想用嘴唇碰阴蒂吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.28,0:07:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,马上就湿了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.34,0:07:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不是很厉害吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.82,0:08:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,变得好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.80,0:08:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,想让我陪你玩吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.94,0:08:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,想被吸得滋滋作响吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.60,0:08:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,吸吮最棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.59,0:08:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,这吸吮的感觉让人受不了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.02,0:08:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,受不了这吸吮吧，来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.17,0:09:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,让我更享受一点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.38,0:09:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,真是让人受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.96,0:10:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,肉棒大得让人受不了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.62,0:10:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,想狠狠地蹭在丝袜上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.76,0:10:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,难道不想在丝袜上尽情摩擦吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.98,0:10:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,想要丝袜想要得不行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.24,0:10:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害的肉棒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.42,0:10:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,快要射了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.58,0:10:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,想射在丝袜上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.66,0:10:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.64,0:11:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,看吧看吧，快乐的事还在后头呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.98,0:11:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,射了可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.28,0:11:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.36,0:11:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,全部都想要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.98,0:11:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,全部都最棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.16,0:11:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.21,0:11:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,想射得不得了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.06,0:11:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,想狠狠地蹭在丝袜上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.26,0:11:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,想在丝袜上尽情摩擦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.58,0:12:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不想让胯下被摩擦吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.62,0:12:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,这样看起来更舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.28,0:12:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,想这样撸动吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.54,0:12:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,胯下这里很热吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.06,0:12:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,想在丝袜上尽情摩擦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.80,0:13:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,想在丝袜上尽情摩擦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.58,0:13:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,想在这里用肉棒蹭来蹭去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.18,0:13:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,鸡巴一抖一抖的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.08,0:13:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,居然抖成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.17,0:13:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,真是拿你没办法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.94,0:13:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,真是没救了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.50,0:13:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.87,0:13:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,胯下蹭在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.98,0:13:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,想在丝袜上尽情摩擦吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.62,0:13:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,射出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.42,0:13:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,想怎么做？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.38,0:14:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,想在胯下这里这样摩擦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.20,0:14:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,想用丝袜这样给你撸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.12,0:14:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,胯下很热吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.80,0:14:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.84,0:14:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,想在丝袜上尽情摩擦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.88,0:14:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,忍不住了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.98,0:15:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.84,0:15:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,变得不得了了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.02,0:15:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,想蹭在这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.20,0:15:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,想在丝袜上尽情摩擦吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.60,0:15:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,在丝袜上尽情蹭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.72,0:15:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,在丝袜上尽情蹭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.07,0:15:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,变得好硬了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.42,0:15:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,忍不住了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.61,0:15:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,在这种地方蹭来蹭去的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.68,0:16:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,在屁股上尽情摩擦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.98,0:16:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,来，整个屁股
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.06,0:16:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,屁股上都变得黏糊糊的了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.36,0:16:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,想漏出来想得不得了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.40,0:16:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,但是变得想要了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.48,0:16:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,想要吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.38,0:16:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,来，给我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.88,0:16:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,全部给我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.08,0:16:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,全部给我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.04,0:17:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,变得想要了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.14,0:17:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,在丝袜上尽情摩擦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.70,0:17:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,好多精液
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.48,0:17:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,在丝袜上尽情摩擦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.78,0:18:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.37,0:18:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,好热的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.69,0:18:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,在丝袜上尽情摩擦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.72,0:19:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,碰到热的地方了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.40,0:19:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,屁股上满满的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.42,0:19:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,变得湿哒哒的了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.37,0:19:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,碰到热的地方了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.58,0:19:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,变得想要了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.86,0:20:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.98,0:21:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,好多精液
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.81,0:21:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,变得想要了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.54,0:21:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,变得想要了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.94,0:21:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好多精液
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.42,0:21:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,好多精液
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.08,0:22:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,胯下让人受不了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.42,0:22:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,是生肉棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.58,0:22:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,生肉棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.20,0:23:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,快要射了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.98,0:23:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.74,0:23:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么流出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.22,0:24:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,已经可以了哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.50,0:24:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,已经可以了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.00,0:25:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.24,0:26:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,还差一点
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.06,0:26:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,还差一点
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.00,0:26:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,想射精液没
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.72,0:27:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,还差一点
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.46,0:30:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,肉棒变得硬邦邦的了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.50,0:30:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,又变得硬邦邦的了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.70,0:30:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不行，是这个哦
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.94,0:31:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,好多精液
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.66,0:31:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,想射出来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.56,0:31:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,可以全都射在我嘴里吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.16,0:31:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,真的很舒服吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.25,0:32:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,好多精液
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.06,0:32:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,射在我嘴里...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.14,0:32:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,痛吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.16,0:32:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不行，已经出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.41,0:33:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不行什么不行，给我好好忍着
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.70,0:33:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,不忍耐可不行  你是想射了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.64,0:33:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,看啊，不想在丝袜上尽情摩擦吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.08,0:33:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我不允许就不行
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.08,0:33:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你就这么射了真的好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.76,0:33:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,看啊，还没蹭够吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.58,0:33:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,要从屁股开始蹭吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.26,0:33:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,这下该怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.46,0:34:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,在丝袜上用力蹭着
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.66,0:34:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,好多精液啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.38,0:34:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,乳头好满
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.40,0:34:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,乳头快受不了了，真的！
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.29,0:34:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.10,0:34:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,真的很痛啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.56,0:35:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,要是射出精液弄脏了，我可是会让你哭的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.46,0:35:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,蹭到了好多
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.04,0:35:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,已经湿了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.72,0:39:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,没错，变态
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.71,0:39:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,射好多
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.64,0:39:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,好多落在丝袜上
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.08,0:39:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.66,0:39:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,啊，马上就勃起了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.34,0:39:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,想要
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.40,0:39:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,想要
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.88,0:39:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,变大了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.29,0:39:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,肉棒
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.61,0:39:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,变态肉棒
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.66,0:40:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,第一发
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.96,0:40:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,在这丝袜上尽情摩擦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.00,0:40:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢真空丝袜吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.18,0:40:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,真的给我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.30,0:40:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.64,0:40:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,射出来舒服吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.62,0:40:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,溢出来好多舒服吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.12,0:41:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,来，想全都射上去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.68,0:41:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,弄脏丝袜也没关系吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.24,0:41:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,全都射上去吧，来
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.04,0:41:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,就算射好多也不会弄脏
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.84,0:41:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉不错
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.96,0:41:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,射了好多出来
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.36,0:41:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,再来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.87,0:41:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,再来一次，我帮你穿上丝袜哦
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.78,0:41:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,丝袜，丝袜...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.19,0:41:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,丝袜...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.30,0:41:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,好像很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.42,0:42:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.26,0:42:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,肉棒，慢慢来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.73,0:43:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.74,0:43:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我说过如果被弄睡着了，
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.64,0:43:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,会有好事的对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.90,0:43:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你想说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.10,0:43:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,是想让我陪你玩吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.56,0:43:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,看看
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.22,0:43:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,真的很能忍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.38,0:43:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,在睡觉吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.22,0:44:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,装睡的话要怎么办呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.90,0:44:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,想让我玩弄你吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.38,0:44:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,难道肉棒已经硬了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.56,0:44:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,呐，是硬着肉棒在等我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.20,0:44:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,等我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.72,0:44:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,真乖
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.30,0:44:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,今天也尽情陪你玩玩吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.85,0:44:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.13,0:44:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那根肉棒
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.70,0:44:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不是很帅气嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.11,0:44:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,是在等着被脚踩吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.13,0:44:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,被狠狠踩踏很舒服吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.26,0:44:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,好好感受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.41,0:44:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,被我踩着要说谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.95,0:44:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服是吧，看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.28,0:44:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,好好陪你玩玩
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.18,0:44:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,狠狠地碾压你
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.28,0:45:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,乳头
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.36,0:45:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,乳头被踩扁了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.50,0:45:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,看，变硬了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.48,0:45:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,乳头
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.46,0:45:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.67,0:45:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,这里也是
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.89,0:45:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,难道全身都是敏感带吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.96,0:45:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,看，兴奋了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.23,0:45:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,看得到我的内裤吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.68,0:45:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.70,0:45:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,来，尽情兴奋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.51,0:45:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,然后让肉棒硬得邦邦的
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.36,0:45:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,让我开心一点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.32,0:45:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你会让我开心吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.24,0:45:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,用肉棒来证明
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.60,0:45:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,看到我这副样子不可能不兴奋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.36,0:46:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,硬到什么程度了？
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.79,0:46:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,才硬成这副德行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.60,0:46:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你在搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.20,0:46:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,想要更痛一点的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.48,0:46:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,还想被我的脚踩得更狠吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.80,0:46:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.42,0:46:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.73,0:46:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,看啊，用力碾压
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.47,0:46:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,想让我把蛋蛋都踩爆吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.94,0:46:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,来，来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.86,0:46:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.78,0:46:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,还要吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.91,0:46:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,看啊，看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.81,0:46:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,来，好好感受
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.62,0:46:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,看，很舒服吧，肉棒
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.42,0:46:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,受不了了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.50,0:46:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.41,0:46:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,蛋蛋要踩爆咯
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.47,0:47:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,要是废掉了该怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.44,0:47:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.80,0:47:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,那表情真是让人受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.38,0:47:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,再来，看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.30,0:47:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,让我看看那种表情
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.51,0:47:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.61,0:47:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.25,0:47:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,被踩扁很舒服吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.31,0:47:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,变态
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.54,0:47:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,用脚狠狠践踏你
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.12,0:47:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.00,0:47:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,这根小鸡巴
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.06,0:47:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,连踩的价值都没有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.61,0:47:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,鸡巴到底在哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.13,0:47:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.76,0:47:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你那根小鸡巴
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.07,0:47:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是一开始就是扁的？
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.60,0:47:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,看，蛋蛋痛吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.74,0:47:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.46,0:47:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,看，要踩烂咯
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.57,0:47:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,看啊，你的蛋蛋正被我的双脚踩着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.93,0:47:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,好开心
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.72,0:47:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,看，兴奋吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.33,0:48:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,看，和我的内裤一起
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.80,0:48:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.55,0:48:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我可是特意为你腾出时间来陪你玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.72,0:48:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,真是没用的鸡巴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.54,0:48:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.18,0:48:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,别让我失望啊
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.54,0:48:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,来，好好撸起来
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.11,0:48:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,看着我的脚
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.58,0:48:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,撸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.65,0:48:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.12,0:48:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,和这内裤一起
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.88,0:48:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,就在我眼前，尽情地撸动
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.63,0:48:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,没出息的鸡巴
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.40,0:48:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.44,0:48:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,让它勃起得更厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.81,0:48:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,让肉棒勃起
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.58,0:50:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,看，变大了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.22,0:50:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,看到我这个样子，不可能不变大吧
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.89,0:50:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.94,0:50:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,想在这里狠狠地插进来吗？，你
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.94,0:50:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,好小
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.96,0:50:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,把肉棒拿出来
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.91,0:50:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.62,0:50:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,来，把肉棒掏出来
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.30,0:50:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,直接碰会怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.06,0:50:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,硬邦邦的
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.57,0:50:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,肉棒变得这么硬了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.74,0:50:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.22,0:50:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,被丝袜夹着
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.12,0:50:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,真是奢侈的肉棒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.82,0:51:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,被我的丝袜双脚夹着
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.50,0:51:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉很粗糙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.20,0:51:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.56,0:51:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,这个，看
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.36,0:51:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,想尽情撸动的话，我就好好帮你撸
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.90,0:51:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是忍着流出来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.34,0:51:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,看啊，有那么舒服吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.82,0:51:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,要是再帮你撸得厉害点，这肉棒会变成什么样呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.70,0:51:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,会变得更大吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.50,0:51:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,还能更大吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.68,0:52:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,帮我撸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.76,0:52:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,还能更努力吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.36,0:52:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,要滴下黏糊糊的液体了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.58,0:52:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.96,0:52:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.54,0:52:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,好暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.20,0:52:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,黏糊糊地滴下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.86,0:52:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗？，真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.14,0:52:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.11,0:52:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.32,0:52:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,被狠狠地摩擦着呢，你的肉棒
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.04,0:52:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,既然这样就让它更硬一点
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.00,0:53:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,来让我看看，让我看肉棒变得更厉害的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.50,0:53:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,看，用力蹭
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.06,0:53:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.92,0:53:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,想要更多吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.92,0:53:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,想看吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.36,0:53:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,想要吧
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.86,0:55:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,知道在这里射了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.81,0:55:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,是，好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.74,0:56:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,啊，摩擦着
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.64,0:56:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,已经被摩擦着了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.16,0:58:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,停下来
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.26,0:58:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.90,0:58:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,很享受奶子吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.90,0:58:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,到底在干什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:58:38.66,0:58:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,那么糟糕吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.96,0:58:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.36,0:59:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,让你休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.47,0:59:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,好喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:59:31.38,0:59:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不行哦，还没好
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.05,0:59:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,让我多享受一下
Dialogue: 0,0:59:39.54,0:59:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,还没结束呢
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.04,0:59:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,让它更硬一点
Dialogue: 0,0:59:47.01,0:59:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你会让我开心的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.48,0:59:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:59:51.46,0:59:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,也就这种程度啊，你的肉棒
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.80,0:59:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,喂，我可没让你停，看
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.10,1:00:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢丝袜吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.32,1:00:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我会帮你好好蹭的
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.02,1:00:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,用力撸起来
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.44,1:00:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,就在我眼前用力撸
Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.00,1:00:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,想把这里塞满
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.48,1:00:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛啊，奶子
Dialogue: 0,1:00:48.08,1:00:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,在我的丝袜上撸你的肉棒
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.54,1:00:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,那个，尽情地撸
Dialogue: 0,1:01:09.68,1:01:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,肉棒变尖了吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:01:29.64,1:01:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:02:04.84,1:02:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:02:06.00,1:02:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,鸡巴，鸡巴
Dialogue: 0,1:02:12.36,1:02:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,尽情地撸吧
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.24,1:02:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,鸡巴硬邦邦地被蹭着
Dialogue: 0,1:02:38.30,1:02:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好像要射了
Dialogue: 0,1:03:07.98,1:03:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,真的要射了
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.11,1:03:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不行哦
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.54,1:05:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,1:05:20.43,1:05:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,肉棒，真的硬得不得了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.80,1:05:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,肉棒，怎么办
Dialogue: 0,1:05:30.52,1:05:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,已经不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:31.50,1:05:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,已经不行了吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:05:33.32,1:05:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,已经不行了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.97,1:05:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:05:51.78,1:05:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,肉棒，肉棒
Dialogue: 0,1:05:54.55,1:05:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,肉棒，射了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:58.64,1:05:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,已经不行了吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:05:59.56,1:06:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,突然就不行了？
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.28,1:06:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,已经受不了了
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.84,1:06:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,受不了了吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:06:49.94,1:06:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,糟糕，要射了
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.38,1:07:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,已经射了吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.90,1:07:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,明明要射了
Dialogue: 0,1:07:05.37,1:07:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,已经空了吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.22,1:07:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,射出来了吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:07:12.94,1:07:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,射了好多啊
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.10,1:07:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,就那么喜欢丝袜吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:07:19.60,1:07:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,那，下次再尽情玩吧
Dialogue: 0,1:07:44.00,1:07:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀，这边也要舔吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:07:48.00,1:07:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,今天，给你看小穴了吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.68,1:07:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,想要奖励吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:07:54.76,1:07:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,是，想要
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.46,1:07:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,1:08:00.86,1:08:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,好好看着
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.78,1:08:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,要好好撸哦
Dialogue: 0,1:08:06.78,1:08:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,看，现在
Dialogue: 0,1:08:11.54,1:08:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,再凑近点看
Dialogue: 0,1:08:16.64,1:08:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,射了吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:08:19.61,1:08:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,射出来了
Dialogue: 0,1:08:23.28,1:08:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,好好看着小穴哦
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.75,1:08:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,撸起来
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.66,1:08:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,想要奖励的吧，你们
Dialogue: 0,1:08:32.39,1:08:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是，想要奖励
Dialogue: 0,1:08:35.00,1:08:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你们勃起了呢
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.07,1:08:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,好好变大
Dialogue: 0,1:08:39.52,1:08:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,兴奋吧
Dialogue: 0,1:08:42.84,1:08:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,让肉棒涨满
Dialogue: 0,1:08:49.22,1:08:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,看，尽情勃起吧
Dialogue: 0,1:08:51.27,1:08:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你们也看着小穴
Dialogue: 0,1:08:54.86,1:08:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,肉棒变成什么样了
Dialogue: 0,1:08:57.76,1:09:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是硬邦邦的吗？，真结实
Dialogue: 0,1:09:00.98,1:09:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,就那么喜欢吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:09:03.90,1:09:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,最喜欢被这样加倍欺负吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:09:08.28,1:09:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,很开心吧
Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.66,1:09:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,开心
Dialogue: 0,1:09:10.86,1:09:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,被大家责备
Dialogue: 0,1:09:14.76,1:09:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,今天也来玩玩吧
Dialogue: 0,1:09:18.34,1:09:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.21,1:09:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,请践踏我
Dialogue: 0,1:09:21.02,1:09:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,那就尽情践踏你吧，来
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.10,1:09:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,1:09:30.00,1:09:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,这样
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.01,1:09:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,这边呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:09:37.24,1:09:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,好大的肉棒呢
Dialogue: 0,1:09:57.50,1:10:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,不给奖励哦
Dialogue: 0,1:10:02.54,1:10:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,1:10:04.91,1:10:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,变得更奇怪一点
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.52,1:10:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,更深地感受我
Dialogue: 0,1:10:14.30,1:10:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,为我变得疯狂吧
Dialogue: 0,1:10:30.44,1:10:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,1:10:35.90,1:10:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,变得想射了
Dialogue: 0,1:10:37.42,1:10:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,变得硬邦邦的了
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.44,1:10:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,好像马上就要射了，没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:10:52.88,1:10:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,啊，耳朵
Dialogue: 0,1:10:55.60,1:10:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,啊，很舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,1:10:57.83,1:11:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,这可是我正在帮你撸的脚哦
Dialogue: 0,1:11:02.72,1:11:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:11:11.40,1:11:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,越来越硬了
Dialogue: 0,1:11:14.37,1:11:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,越来越硬了呢，肉棒
Dialogue: 0,1:11:20.94,1:11:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,啊，让我看看
Dialogue: 0,1:11:22.03,1:11:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,变得更硬一点
Dialogue: 0,1:11:23.92,1:11:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,让我看看你对我的屁股有多兴奋
Dialogue: 0,1:11:27.04,1:11:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,对着我的屁股
Dialogue: 0,1:11:32.04,1:11:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你也让我看看兴奋的样子
Dialogue: 0,1:11:34.30,1:11:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你也很兴奋对吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:11:36.96,1:11:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,这边的肉棒也好色
Dialogue: 0,1:11:40.78,1:11:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,变得更硬一点
Dialogue: 0,1:11:43.52,1:11:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,更加更加，这个
Dialogue: 0,1:11:47.20,1:11:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,变硬了
Dialogue: 0,1:11:49.58,1:11:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,尽情地蹭在我的脚上吧
Dialogue: 0,1:11:55.46,1:11:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,受不了
Dialogue: 0,1:11:58.94,1:12:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,想直接蹭想得不得了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:12:01.70,1:12:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,变得疯狂吧
Dialogue: 0,1:12:03.57,1:12:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,想要吧，我的这双脚
Dialogue: 0,1:12:08.76,1:12:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,全都给你
Dialogue: 0,1:12:22.78,1:12:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害，隔着裤子都这么硬了
Dialogue: 0,1:12:26.22,1:12:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,会变成什么样呢，这根好色的肉棒
Dialogue: 0,1:12:29.34,1:12:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,要射在裤子里了吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:12:31.58,1:12:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,快要射了吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:12:33.24,1:12:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,不行哦
Dialogue: 0,1:12:34.25,1:12:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,看，要射了吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:12:39.42,1:12:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,还完全不想射吧
Dialogue: 0,1:12:44.02,1:12:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你们
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.88,1:12:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,求我啊，想让我直接摸吧
Dialogue: 0,1:12:55.18,1:12:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,尽情地摸
Dialogue: 0,1:12:57.90,1:13:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,把肉棒拿出来
Dialogue: 0,1:13:10.66,1:13:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,1:13:12.50,1:13:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,被勾住了
Dialogue: 0,1:13:27.62,1:13:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,继续摸
Dialogue: 0,1:13:52.02,1:13:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,变得好痛
Dialogue: 0,1:14:21.08,1:14:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,1:14:53.74,1:14:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,1:14:57.68,1:15:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了，肉棒
Dialogue: 0,1:15:28.74,1:15:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,射了哦
Dialogue: 0,1:15:35.88,1:15:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧来吧，把肉棒蹭过来，蹭我身上
Dialogue: 0,1:15:50.28,1:15:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,看，很舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,1:16:00.30,1:16:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,尽情地蹭吧
Dialogue: 0,1:16:03.56,1:16:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,看，还要更多吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:16:04.80,1:16:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,还要更多
Dialogue: 0,1:16:31.48,1:16:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,快要炸了吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:17:20.08,1:17:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,啊，好软，好可爱
Dialogue: 0,1:17:28.66,1:17:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,真美味
Dialogue: 0,1:17:31.04,1:17:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,啊，真舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:17:37.58,1:17:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这边比较老实呢
Dialogue: 0,1:17:39.50,1:17:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,1:17:43.78,1:17:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,无论如何腰都...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:24.98,1:18:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,1:27:23.59,1:27:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样射出来可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:27:27.64,1:27:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,还没好哦
Dialogue: 0,1:27:32.64,1:27:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,还得再忍耐一下才行
Dialogue: 0,1:27:37.44,1:27:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,给我吧，肉棒
Dialogue: 0,1:27:42.40,1:27:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我还没享受够呢
Dialogue: 0,1:27:48.52,1:27:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,实际上我只是要让这根肉棒好好取悦我而已，你明白的吧
Dialogue: 0,1:27:55.36,1:27:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,现在可不是擅自射的时候
Dialogue: 0,1:28:16.76,1:28:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:28:48.16,1:28:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,啊，加油
Dialogue: 0,1:28:50.00,1:28:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,肉棒真好吃
Dialogue: 0,1:29:01.88,1:29:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,肉棒给我
Dialogue: 0,1:29:05.07,1:29:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,给我进到小穴里来
Dialogue: 0,1:29:45.36,1:29:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,1:29:55.50,1:29:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,1:29:59.74,1:30:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,1:30:45.96,1:30:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,还要一会？
Dialogue: 0,1:30:47.93,1:30:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,还得再忍耐一下哦
Dialogue: 0,1:32:36.18,1:32:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:32:37.79,1:32:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,肉棒，让人受不了
Dialogue: 0,1:32:41.54,1:32:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀，射好多
Dialogue: 0,1:32:43.30,1:32:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,射好多在我小穴里
Dialogue: 0,1:32:47.70,1:32:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,射好多在我小穴里
Dialogue: 0,1:34:04.82,1:34:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,肉棒，射好多出来
Dialogue: 0,1:34:09.86,1:34:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,射好多在我小穴里
Dialogue: 0,1:34:17.82,1:34:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,还不够
Dialogue: 0,1:35:04.88,1:35:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,还差一点
Dialogue: 0,1:35:35.56,1:35:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,哪个？
Dialogue: 0,1:35:40.80,1:35:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,别动啊
Dialogue: 0,1:35:52.66,1:35:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我的小穴里满满的
Dialogue: 0,1:35:54.79,1:35:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,1:38:46.46,1:38:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,来，尽情地撸
Dialogue: 0,1:38:57.44,1:38:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,痛吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:41:51.46,1:41:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,再一次
Dialogue: 0,1:42:59.76,1:43:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,啊，肉棒最棒了！
Dialogue: 0,1:43:01.99,1:43:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,给我好多肉棒！
Dialogue: 0,1:43:04.70,1:43:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,肉棒！
Dialogue: 0,1:43:06.90,1:43:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,啊，全部给我！
Dialogue: 0,1:45:31.76,1:45:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,高潮了
Dialogue: 0,1:45:53.20,1:45:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我的小穴
Dialogue: 0,1:46:09.56,1:46:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:46:18.00,1:46:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,对，我的小穴
Dialogue: 0,1:46:24.56,1:46:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,没想到能忍住
Dialogue: 0,1:46:27.18,1:46:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,1:46:30.58,1:46:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,给你一脚！
Dialogue: 0,1:47:57.18,1:47:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,好累
Dialogue: 0,1:48:08.36,1:48:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,好暖和

